On March 18, 2013, Woods announced that he and Olympic gold medal skier Lindsey Vonn were dating.[210] They split up in May 2015.[211] From November 2016 to August 2017, Woods was rumored in a relationship with stylist Kristin Smith.[212] Woods announced in November 2017 that he was in a relationship with restaurant manager Erica Herman, following speculation about their relationship that began the month prior.[citation needed]
